# 🧠 Vector-Based Thought Processing - Spiralverse RAG Enhancement

Status: Living Document | Version: 1.0.0-draft | Last Updated: January 6, 2026
Integration Layer: This document describes how to add memory-augmented intelligence to the Spiralverse Protocol via vector embeddings and RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation).
